plot: The Regents are under attack and several have been assassinated. It's up to the Warehosuse 13 crew to thwart the current attack by an unknown organization equipped with artifacts.

In the past year, several Regents have died. The Warehouse 13 crew's capture of Sally Stukowski leads them into discovering a plot to kill off more Regents via a spray paint artifact. As team members struggle not only to keep the Regents alive in a steadily dissolving building but themselves alive as well, Steve reaches a point of professional crisis when Mrs. Frederic takes over Sally's interrogation, and Pete encounters the surprise of his life.—statmanjeff
